components.name: HighlightReelComponent
components.templateData:
<swiper [slidesPerView]="1.5" [spaceBetween]="24">
    <ng-template *ngIf="(oversizeItem$ | async) as item" swiperSlide>
        <app-touchable-a class="item" [title]="item.title" [backgroundUrl]="item.backgroundUrl"></app-touchable-a>
    </ng-template>
    <ng-template *ngIf="(largeItem$ | async) as item" swiperSlide>
        <app-touchable-b class="item"  [title]="item.title" [backgroundUrl]="item.backgroundUrl"></app-touchable-b>
    </ng-template>
    <ng-template *ngFor="let item of wideItems$ | async" swiperSlide>
        <app-touchable-c class="item" [title]="item.title" [backgroundUrl]="item.backgroundUrl"></app-touchable-c>
    </ng-template>
    <ng-template *ngFor="let item of items$ | async" swiperSlide>
        <app-touchable-d class="item" [title]="item.title" [backgroundUrl]="item.backgroundUrl"></app-touchable-d>
    </ng-template>
</swiper>
